{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_02_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 プライドの塊",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirが星見プロに移籍して、数ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few months after LizNoir’s transfer to Hoshimi Productions",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "悪いわね、日曜日に呼び出して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to make you come out on a Sunday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "かまいませんよ\nそれより、折り入っての相談って？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not a problem.\nWhat did you want to discuss?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの今後について、方向性を決めたいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s about the direction of LizNoir going forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いきなりですね……\n現状に何か不満でもあるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ that’s a sudden…\nAre you unhappy with the way things are?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.366666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、LizNoirは愛とこころが加入して\n以前より注目されたし、仕事も増えたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. Adding Ai and Kokoro\nhas increased LizNoir’s exposure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.966666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "愛とこころのキャラクターは親しみを持ちやすい\nそれによって、ファン層が拡大したのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They both have approachable personalities‚\nwhich have expanded our fanbase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、それに四人になって仕事内容にも幅が出たし\n今、リズノワの評価は業界でも急上昇中ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it’s really increased LizNoir’s range of work.\nThe response from other people in this industry has been very positive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "オファーが多くて、選ぶのに苦労しているくらいだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re getting so many offers‚ it’s been a headache choosing which to accept.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そう、それよ、仕事の選択\nこれからはそれが大切になると思うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s exactly what I wanted to discuss.\nChoosing the right offers is going to be very important going forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "勢いのある今だからこそ、LizNoirが\nより上のステージを目指すチャンスじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ LizNoir is riding the tide of momentum.\nThis is our chance to climb higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "そのために、リーダーとして何をすればいいのか\n最近、よく考えているのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And recently it’s made me think carefully about\nwhat I should do as the leader of the group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスと歌のレッスンはもちろんちゃんとやる\nでも、もっと上に行くにはプラスアルファが必要だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ we won’t compromise with our dance and singing lessons.\nBut we need something more than that if we want to keep climbing higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "歌やダンス以外だと……\nうーん、そうだな、グラビアの仕事は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something other than song and dance…\nHmm… What about photo posing for gravure?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "今までと同じような仕事じゃ弱いわ\nもっとインパクトのある仕事はない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s still the same kind of work as before.\nIsn’t there something that would make more of a splash?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あると言えば、ありますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I suppose there is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、今の間は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you hesitating?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "面白い仕事だけど、莉央さんには難しいかな\nと思って返事を保留にしてた案件が一つ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s an interesting offer‚ but it might be a tough one for you.\nThat’s why I haven’t given them an answer yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "……私には難しい、ですって？\nどんな内容なのよ？　教えなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A tough one for me?\nWhat do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それが、結構大きい話なんです\n外では詳細は話せないので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a pretty long story‚\nand best not talk about it out here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ、事務所に行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very well‚ let’s go to the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": 120.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "テーマパークのハロウィンイベント？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Halloween event at a theme park?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ゲストの一人として\n参加してほしいというオファーです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. They’re inviting you to\nparticipate solo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワではなく\n神崎莉央への単独オファーなんです。場所は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The offer is for you personally‚\nnot for LizNoir. And the location…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "え？　それって国内有数のテーマパークじゃない！\nよくテレビCMも流れてるわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s one of the biggest theme parks in the country!\nI see their ads on TV all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "私もここは大好きなのよ。葵と何度か遊びに\n行ったこともあるわ。素敵よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a great place.\nI’ve gone there with Aoi many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "好きだったんですね……。たぶんハロウィンの期間中は\n莉央さんもCMに出ることになると思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… The offer probably involves\nyou appearing in their commercials around Halloween time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "なんで保留にしてたのよ！　すぐに受けて！\n他に話がいったら大変じゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why haven’t you answered them? Accept it now!\nBefore they look for someone else!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それはさっき外でも話題に出たけど\n莉央さんにはちょっと厳しいかと悩んでいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ like I said while we were outside‚\nit might be a tough one for you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ハロウィンイベントだし、当然、莉央さんにも\n仮装……というかコスプレをしてもらうことになります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a Halloween event‚ so you’ll be expected to dress up…\nBasically‚ cosplay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "仮装くらいなんでもないわ。私が今まで何十種類の\nステージ衣装を着たと思っているの？　舐めないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How many stage costumes do you think I’ve put on in my career?\nDressing up is nothing to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "コスプレは変わった衣装を着るだけじゃないですよ\n化粧もするし、キャラになりきらないといけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cosplay isn’t just about putting on a costume.\nYou’ll also have to put on makeup and act in character.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "愛やこころはともかく、そういうのって\n莉央さんは抵抗あるんじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s one thing to ask Ai and Kokoro to do it‚\nbut I thought you might object to this sort of work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "……私が後輩達よりも、仕事の幅が狭いと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying that I have less range than my juniors?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そうじゃなくて\n俺は単に向き、不向きの話を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not what I mean‚ it’s just that‚ you know‚\neveryone has their strengths and weaknesses—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "この仕事、受けてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Accept the offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "え、ちょっと、仕事の内容も聞かずに？\n向こうのスタッフさん達の話を聞いてからでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ without even listening to the details?\nLet’s talk to them first‚ know more about the job…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
