      "text": "もう十分に聞いたわ\nどんな格好をしようが、私は私よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve heard all I needed to know.\nNo matter how I dress‚ I’m myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "観客全員を、LizNoirの神崎莉央の魅力で\n圧倒してやるわ",
